<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center">……</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200922/c666391f7ac640a485d643cf4064c03e.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">金泽古镇 曹巨波/摄</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200922/58fb1d885ead4da28824f1ba74f48807.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">枫泾古镇 曹巨波/摄</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在<strong>曹巨波</strong>的眼中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">江南充满着烟火气</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">特别是在那水乡古镇</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">街头巷尾的老商铺</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">石路两旁叫卖的各色小吃</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">喝茶的、闲逛的、画画的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还有自行车经过时</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">发出的叮铃叮铃的声音……</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这样的生活气息深深地吸引着他</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200922/5ae1489d0d754721b8a0255801cf64e1.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">绍兴安昌古镇 曹巨波/摄</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200922/491cfd3d6c554024ba1aef9e90f0feed.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">枫泾古镇 曹巨波/摄</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200922/1534125807fd4e59a1ad9ed31f3b6a37.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">枫泾古镇 曹巨波/摄</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200922/0757905a7bba46178725eef8a0d1846e.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">枫泾古镇 曹巨波/摄</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200922/39202e2e4beb457b9e486cd267745b25.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">枫泾古镇 曹巨波/摄</span></img></p>
