<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200922/d2f9b9952ea24da6a2c1eb775fd76226.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">【对视】青海茫崖艾肯泉 徐骞/摄</p>
